3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with multi-channel data and presentation attacks. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also possible as the paper deals with anti-spoofing in face recognition systems. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with feature extraction and domain adaptation techniques.
